videos.description: Matt Haarms locks up Deandre Ayton by swatting his turnaround jumper into the crowd in the first half.
videos.headline: Purdue's Haarms shuts down Ayton

videos.description: Allonzo Trier soars through the air on his way to an emphatic one-handed jam for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier rocks the rim with monster slam

videos.description: Matt Haarms gets the dish from Dakota Mathias and slams it home for the Boilermakers.
videos.headline: Purdue's Haarms throws down two-handed jam

videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets the lob from half-court and finishes strong for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Ayton throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Matt Haarms sends Allonzo Trier's shot flying in the second half for the Boilermakers.
videos.headline: Haarms shuts down the Wildcats again

videos.description: In the seventh place game at the Battle 4 Atlantis, the No. 18 Boilermakers hand the No. 2 Wildcats their third loss in three days with an 89-64 defeat.
videos.headline: Purdue dominates Arizona
